allure is a 2014 independent feature film written , directed and edited by vladan nikolic .   based on true stories , filmmakers and performers - actors and non-actors - worked together to flesh out the story and protagonists .   all scenes and dialogue in the film were improvised .   some scenes were shot with actors participating in the actual occupy wall street protests of 2011 and 2012 .   the film premiered at the 2014 black nights film festival in tallinn , estonia , where it was nominated for best north american independent feature film , and had a limited release in the us in march 2015 , followed by on video-on-demand and online streaming in the fall of 2015 .